1
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:19,500
You think you could
deceive me, Barrel Rider?

2
00:00:22,220 --> 00:00:24,460
You have come from Lake Town.

3
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:30,539
This is some sordid
skee-mat between these filthy

4
00:00:30,551 --> 00:00:34,460
dwarfs and those miserable
top-trading lake-men.

5
00:00:36,010 --> 00:00:42,460
Those sniveling cowards with
their long bows and black arrows.

6
00:00:43,110 --> 00:00:47,460
Perhaps it is time I paid them a visit.

7
00:00:47,461 --> 00:00:49,460
Oh, no.

8
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,399
This isn't their fault!

9
00:00:52,461 --> 00:00:53,460
Wait!

10
00:00:53,461 --> 00:00:56,460
You cannot go to Lake Town!

11
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,460
You care about them, do you?

12
00:01:01,461 --> 00:01:02,460
Good.

13
00:01:02,461 --> 00:01:06,460
Then you can watch them die.

14
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:12,499
Here!

15
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:18,199
You witless worm!

16
00:01:21,461 --> 00:01:26,460
I am king under the mountain.

17
00:01:26,461 --> 00:01:28,460
This is not your kingdom.

18
00:01:29,061 --> 00:01:30,460
These are dwarf lands.

19
00:01:31,961 --> 00:01:33,460
This is dwarf gold.

20
00:01:35,861 --> 00:01:38,460
And we will have our revenge.

21
00:02:15,660 --> 00:02:16,160
Revenge!

22
00:02:17,561 --> 00:02:18,460
Revenge!

23
00:02:20,161 --> 00:02:26,160
I will show you revenge!

24
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:52,360
Listen to me!

25
00:02:54,261 --> 00:02:56,360
Do you not know what is coming?

26
00:02:58,060 --> 00:03:00,460
What have we done?

27
00:03:00,861 --> 00:03:04,960
I am fire!

28
00:03:06,461 --> 00:03:10,460
I am...

29
00:03:10,910 --> 00:03:12,460
Death!

